{"tid":1711890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略分析]為什麼中大二號橋為警方控制不可？","createTime":"2019-11-12T12:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T13:06:51.000Z","uid":245977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7110d87dd07067b8cf0960421bb77e7ae585ae","tid":1711890,"uid":245977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"如果你睇吓地圖，中大二號橋係唯一一個喺馬料水嘅窄位，橫跨全線吐露港公路及東鐵路軌。如果控制二號橋，即系勒緊新界西北所有交通嘅咽喉。所以警方非取不可。歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"044e309a8a2462c57f4b77987a85d457d0edd911","tid":1711890,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"冇咩 只係咁啱"},{"pid":"6f12c20796655cdd737070fedfe9199228d338ce","tid":1711890,"uid":276519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdM5MBf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdM5MBf.jpg&h=8c121079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一張圖就清楚二號橋既戰略價值"},{"pid":"d622a5524783db13a9d79c2b0ca485605226abea","tid":1711890,"uid":245977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"正解，圖中左邊係中大山邊，右邊係吐露港。此狹窄地帶長度不足100米，簡直係新界大西北交通咽喉之地。"}]}